This is the README file for jpgresize, a perl script to
resizes a couple of JPG images simultaniously.

For more information on how to use the script, see the
pod documentation via the command
  
  perldoc jpgresize

or, after installation, view the man pages with
  
  man jpgresize

For instructions on how to install the script, see the
file INSTALL.

Problems, questions, etc. may be sent to flo@goslich-online.de

